[HEADER]
id: spellbook
title: The Grimoire

[CONTENT]
The script rearranges itself as you read.
One sigil repeats beside a margin note:
"Bind the named. Name the bound."
You practice the cadence until the page cools beneath your hands.
You can now cast a binding spell with intent.

[OPTIONS]
close_book | Close the book -> ./library.level

[DIRECTIVES]
input_mode: choice

[OPTION_EFFECTS]
option=close_book add_flag=learned_binding
option=close_book set_value=spell:binding
